WEBVTT

00:00.867 --> 00:04.303
- <i>Previously on</i> The Vampire Diaries...
- Caroline Elizabeth Forbes,

00:04.328 --> 00:06.474
I want you to marry me.

00:06.476 --> 00:09.498
- Yes.
- I've seen that symbol before.

00:09.523 --> 00:12.046
<i>I saw it when I was dead.
This thing that was delivered</i>

00:12.048 --> 00:14.715
<i>with your vault inhabitant?
I think it was made in Hell.</i>

00:14.717 --> 00:17.255
ALARIC: <i>Sirens use mind
control to lure their victims</i>

00:17.280 --> 00:19.594
<i>to their death. Some say
they're messengers of the devil.</i>

00:19.619 --> 00:22.192
We are talking about a living,
breathing thing siren.

00:22.217 --> 00:26.000
The more specific my thoughts are, the
more she can key in on me psychically.

00:26.025 --> 00:28.259
- What does she want with you?
- She wants two loyal soldiers

00:28.283 --> 00:29.313
to keep bringing her supper.

00:29.337 --> 00:30.965
<i>Well, my mind is bonded to hers.</i>

00:30.967 --> 00:32.833
Every moment we spend
together is another moment

00:32.835 --> 00:34.702
she could discover how I feel about you.

00:34.704 --> 00:37.538
Why haven't I seen her before?

00:37.540 --> 00:41.058
- Damon's not gone.
- STEFAN: <i>Yeah, he is. I saw it happen.</i>

00:41.083 --> 00:42.613
He belongs to the siren now.

00:42.638 --> 00:44.245
- I'm Elena.
- I'm Damon.

00:44.247 --> 00:45.780
Don't worry about your brother.

00:45.782 --> 00:46.910
<i>I've taken over</i>

00:46.935 --> 00:48.426
<i>his last mental refuge.</i>

00:48.451 --> 00:50.584
<i>I'm giving it a little remodel.</i>

00:50.586 --> 00:52.687
Hi. What's your name?

00:52.689 --> 00:53.654
I'm Damon.

00:53.656 --> 00:54.889
I'm Sybil.

00:56.492 --> 00:58.059
(tires screech, engine revs)

00:58.061 --> 00:59.593
(water splashes)

01:00.697 --> 01:02.830
(coughs)

01:06.300 --> 01:08.801
(echoing): Dad?

01:08.826 --> 01:11.346
We're gonna be okay. I promise.

01:11.371 --> 01:12.137
Dad!

01:12.139 --> 01:14.306
(gasping)

01:20.147 --> 01:21.880
♪ ♪

